The following package should be installed before RainbruRPG-meta is installed:

* Foswiki
  + Needed : the metaserver is a foswiki's plugin
  + homepage:
    http://foswiki.org
  + download:
    http://foswiki.org/Download/DownloadFoswiki

* XML::LibXML
  + Needed : Perl bindings for libxml2
  + homepage:
    http://search.cpan.org/~shlomif/XML-LibXML-1.94/LibXML.pod
  + download:
    http://search.cpan.org/~shlomif/XML-LibXML-1.94/LibXML.pod
    
* Test::Unit::Procedural
  + Optional : to run unit tests
  + homepage:
    http://search.cpan.org/dist/Test-Unit/lib/Test/Unit/Procedural.pm
  + download:
    http://ftp.easynet.be/pub/CPAN/authors/id/M/MC/MCAST/
